You guys really won?

856
00:41:28,520 --> 00:41:29,200
Yes, we did.

857
00:41:29,200 --> 00:41:30,760
Do you think we’re really good?

858
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:32,520
Do you have any admiration for us?

859
00:41:32,520 --> 00:41:33,800
No, not really.

860
00:41:36,160 --> 00:41:37,280
You’ll have to give me
extra points this time.

861
00:41:42,920 --> 00:41:44,200
Not even a single point.

862
00:41:44,200 --> 00:41:45,560
You’re too stingy.

863
00:41:46,720 --> 00:41:47,800
What’s the use of knowing
how to play games?

864
00:41:51,560 --> 00:41:52,920
These shoes are 1,600 yuan.

865
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:55,134
I won them on my own.

866
00:41:55,506 --> 00:41:57,906
You tell me that
playing games is useless?

867
00:41:58,080 --> 00:41:59,560
I’m kind enough to give you

868
00:41:59,560 --> 00:42:01,000
the title of Game Master.

869
00:42:01,000 --> 00:42:02,120
Besides,

870
00:42:02,120 --> 00:42:03,000
you got help from

871
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:04,880
Lu Miao and Jiang Haoyue.

872
00:42:29,897 --> 00:42:30,977
Why are you here alone?

873
00:42:34,840 --> 00:42:35,880
It’s less crowded

874
00:42:35,880 --> 00:42:36,880
and quieter here.

875
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:40,680
You’re here to get the drums
for the honor guard, right?

876
00:42:41,760 --> 00:42:42,680
I’ll come with you.

877
00:42:45,840 --> 00:42:46,520
Nice shoes.

878
00:42:48,160 --> 00:42:49,600
Thank you for your help.

879
00:42:50,280 --> 00:42:52,680
You’re my friend now.

880
00:42:54,160 --> 00:42:55,120
No need to be so polite.

881
00:42:55,600 --> 00:42:56,440
It’s all for Lu Miao.

882
00:42:57,440 --> 00:42:58,560
For Lu Miao?

883
00:43:06,600 --> 00:43:08,440
Give me that little castle.

884
00:43:08,880 --> 00:43:09,560
Here.

885
00:43:10,160 --> 00:43:10,760
Thank you!

886
00:43:13,920 --> 00:43:14,760
Jiang Haoyue!

887
00:43:16,880 --> 00:43:18,320
Come down and play sand together.

888
00:43:27,209 --> 00:43:28,387
He can’t play,

889
00:43:28,387 --> 00:43:29,800
so why did you ask him?

890
00:43:29,800 --> 00:43:31,320
Who says he can’t play?

891
00:43:31,320 --> 00:43:33,320
I will let him play to show you.

892
00:43:34,120 --> 00:43:34,760
Jiang Haoyue.

893
00:43:34,760 --> 00:43:36,520
Look what I’ve brought you.

894
00:43:37,880 --> 00:43:38,880
Give me your hands.

895
00:43:41,360 --> 00:43:42,160
It’s dirty.

896
00:43:44,400 --> 00:43:46,200
Okay, now we’re the same.

897
00:43:48,320 --> 00:43:50,040
We’re going to make one
even better than theirs.

898
00:43:50,520 --> 00:43:53,520
How about a giant chocolate?

899
00:43:57,600 --> 00:43:58,600
It’s just a square.

900
00:43:58,600 --> 00:43:59,880
What’s so difficult about it?

901
00:43:59,880 --> 00:44:01,040
So what do you want to make?

902
00:44:03,960 --> 00:44:05,000
I’ll help you.

903
00:44:16,120 --> 00:44:18,400
This is worse than the chocolate.

904
00:44:24,787 --> 00:44:29,187
♪There’s a window in my heart♪

905
00:44:29,731 --> 00:44:33,609
♪Open it and there’s light♪

906
00:44:33,997 --> 00:44:38,075
♪Maintain old memories♪

907
00:44:38,272 --> 00:44:40,947
♪That are simple and beautiful♪

908
00:44:43,378 --> 00:44:46,865
♪Time goes by♪

909
00:44:47,315 --> 00:44:51,084
♪Making memories into nets♪

910
00:44:51,962 --> 00:44:58,275
♪That sway with wind in my dream♪

911
00:45:00,153 --> 00:45:04,090
♪I asked about the lifetime♪

912
00:45:04,315 --> 00:45:08,306
♪It would be very long♪

913
00:45:08,953 --> 00:45:12,928
♪I like to share with you what I like♪

914
00:45:12,990 --> 00:45:15,868
♪And what I think is the best♪

915
00:45:17,928 --> 00:45:21,584
♪In this world♪

916
00:45:21,984 --> 00:45:25,847
♪Only you’re like me♪

917
00:45:26,709 --> 00:45:33,362
♪From youth to the end of life♪

918
